---
layout: base.njk
title: Tutorials
description: In-depth technical tutorials on AI, DevOps, and software engineering.
permalink: /articles/
---

<div class="section-header">
  <h1>📚 All Tutorials</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">In-depth technical guides with code examples and architecture patterns.</p>
</div>

<div class="card-grid">
  {%- for article in collections.articles -%}
  <div class="card">
    <span class="tag">{{ article.data.tags[0] if article.data.tags else 'Tutorial' }}</span>
    <h3><a href="{{ article.url | url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ article.data.description }}</p>
    <div class="meta">{{ article.data.date | readableDate }} · {{ article.data.readTime or '8 min read' }}</div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
